Easy going, woods and wind kinda guy, summers I’m on the waters or in the trees. Me and my dog are always together, he’s patient and has lots of great people who can watch him if I’m needed for a time away.  I enjoy technology and figuring out how to make things work.

Senior IT professional experienced in infrastructure, cloud, and technology management. Microsoft Azure and D365FO certified. Proven record of improving business efficiency through automation, reliable infrastructure, and high-quality client/customer service.

    • Strong respect for the importance of discovering and establishing the truth.
    • Proficient in working with log files, including parsing data and using pipes to manage commands
    • Understand core IT building blocks and the importance of correct procedure and process.
    • Data management has been a large part of my work, including databases/queries.
    • Security and confidentiality are achieved through minimal access, deliberate risk evaluation, and appropriate technical and procedural controls.
    • My next objective is to apply this foundation to the field of artificial intelligence.

